	<div class="ui grid maingrid" id="jsDesc">
		<h2 Class="ui horizontal divider header">
			<i class="terminal icon"></i>
			Features of this Project
		</h2>
		<div class="one column row">
			<div class="ui main text container">
				<p>JSTennis is a short, pong-like game created using JavaScript, and HTML5 Canvas Drawing (2D)</p>
				<p>Features include:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Score Keeping and Win/Loss Conditions</li>
					<li>Mouse Tracking for Player Racket Control</li>
					<li>Simple Throttled Paddle AI</li>
					<li>AI which speeds up as the player scores and slows down as it scores</li>
					<li>Gradual increase in ball speed with each hit, promoting a quick resolution of each set.</li>
				</ul>
				<p>Source code for this game can be found
				<a href="https://github.com/NoFoxDevelopment/CV-Updated/blob/master/js/jstennis.js">HERE</a>.</p>
				<p>I used this project to teach myself both simple canvas operations as well as JavaScript fundamentals.</p>
